"lifeSummary":"Когда Lady Agnes Lockwood родилась в 1417 г. в местности локквуд, еркшир, Англия, её отцу по имени Henry de Lockwood было 40 лет, а матери, которую звали Lady Agnes De La Schaw, 42. Она вышла замуж за человека по имени Sir John Anderson около 1438 г. У них было по крайней мере 4 сына и 1 дочь. Она умерла в 1448 г. в местности нюкастл упон тин, нортумбирланд, Англия в возрасте 31 год."},"sm":{"1417–1448":"1417–1448","1404–1434":"1404–1434","1415–1465":"1415–1465","1440–1490":"1440–1490","1442–Male":"1442–Ua Maliu","1444–Female":"1444–Ua Maliu","1446–Male":"1446–Ua Maliu","1448–Male":"1448–Ua Maliu","1378–Male":"1378–Ua Maliu","1375–1486":"1375–1486","1440":"1440","1490":"1490","1448":"1448","1415":"1415","1404":"1404","1446":"1446","1434":"1434","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","about 1438":"e tusa o le 1438","1465":"1465","1442":"1442","ABT 1398":"e tusa o le 1398","1486":"1486","1375":"1375","1417":"1417","Newcastle upon Tyne, Northumberland, England":"Newcastle upon Tyne, Northumberland, Egelani","York, Yorkshire, England":"York, Yorkshire, Egelani, United Kingdom","Bedfordshire, England":"Bedfordshire, Egelani","Lockwood, Yorkshire, England":"Lockwood, Yorkshire, Egelani"},"sk":{"1417–1448":"1417–1448","1404–1434":"1404–1434","1415–1465":"1415–1465","1440–1490":"1440–1490","1442–Male":"1442–Zosnulý","1444–Female":"1444–Zosnulá","1446–Male":"1446–Zosnulý","1448–Male":"1448–Zosnulý","1378–Male":"1378–Zosnulý","1375–1486":"1375–1486","1440":"1440","1490":"1490","1448":"1448","1415":"1415","1404":"1404","1446":"1446","1434":"1434","1444":"1444","1378":"1378","about 1438":"okolo 1438","1465":"1465","1442":"1442","ABT 1398":"okolo 1398","1486":"1486","1375":"1375","1417":"1417","Newcastle upon Tyne, Northumberland, England":"Newcastle upon Tyne, Northumberland, England","York, Yorkshire, England":"York, Yorkshire, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Bedfordshire, England":"Bedfordshire, England","Lockwood, Yorkshire, England":"Lockwood, Yorkshire, England"},"es":{